{
  "info": {
    "name": "Inscripcion Cursos - Semana 1",
    "description": "Coleccion organizada por ROL.\n\nCarpeta 01 ADMIN (auth: admin / Admin2026!)\nCarpeta 02 ESTUDIANTE (auth: estudiante / Estudiante2026!)\nCarpeta 03 Infraestructura (publico)\n\nFlujo completo:\n1. Ejecuta carpeta ADMIN en orden (01 reset -> ... -> 08 errores)\n2. Ejecuta carpeta ESTUDIANTE en orden (01 listar -> ... -> 09 errores)\n3. Verifica en SQL: scripts/consultas-verificacion-oracle.sql (mismo orden)\n\nVariables: baseUrl, adminUser, adminPassword, estudianteUser, estudiantePassword",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "01 - ADMIN",
      "description": "Todo lo que hace el rol ADMIN. Auth Basic heredada: admin / Admin2026!",
      "auth": {
        "type": "basic",
        "basic": [
          { "key": "username", "value": "{{adminUser}}", "type": "string" },
          { "key": "password", "value": "{{adminPassword}}", "type": "string" }
        ]
      },
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "ADMIN 01 - Reset datos prueba",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200 OK', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/reset-pruebas",
            "description": "Limpia inscripciones/cursos y deja 3 cursos (ids 1,2,3).\nEjecutar SIEMPRE antes de una demo nueva.\nSQL: bloque ADMIN 01"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "ADMIN 02 - Listar cursos",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/cursos",
            "description": "Catalogo publico (auth admin tambien funciona).\nEsperado: 200, 3 cursos.\nSQL: bloque ADMIN 02"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "ADMIN 03 - Crear curso Java Cloud",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('201 Created', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(201); });"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Java Cloud Native\",\n  \"instructor\": \"Prof. Silva\",\n  \"duracionHoras\": 45,\n  \"costo\": 175000\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/cursos",
            "description": "Esperado: 201, id 4.\nSQL: bloque ADMIN 03"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "ADMIN 04 - Crear curso Microservicios",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
